      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ESPECIAL HUGO (1) promising type who notched his 1st career success when too good (25.50) at Shepparton last time. Tends to go well off this box draw. Has the inside draw and looks tough to beat here. RONALDO JACK (8) was quickly into stride on debut to score by 0.8 lengths (16.85) at this track over 300m. Boxed wide but has the pace to be prominent. This tougher but looks a leading chance again. ASTON ROCHELLE (7) is better than last start when seventh (24.99) in a Rank Limit - Restricted Win at Sale over 435m. The form from her last run is stacking up nicely. Shapes as one to consider. ELEVENTH SCOTCH (2) is in the mix despite finishing out of the placings here last start.",
